    "description": "<p><span style=\"font-family: 'Trebuchet MS', 'Lucida Sans Unicode', 'Lucida Grande', 'Lucida Sans', Arial, sans-serif\">You can spend <strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; scrollbar-width: thin; scrollbar-color: var(--color-scrollbar) var(--color-scrollbar-track);\">2 AP</strong> to censure </span>all Celestials and Fiends of your choice<span style=\"font-family: 'Trebuchet MS', 'Lucida Sans Unicode', 'Lucida Grande', 'Lucida Sans', Arial, sans-serif\"> who can see or hear you within 5 Spaces.</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; scrollbar-width: thin; scrollbar-color: var(--color-scrollbar) var(--color-scrollbar-track); margin: 0.5em 0px; color: rgb(25, 24, 19); font-family: 'Trebuchet MS', 'Lucida Sans Unicode', 'Lucida Grande', 'Lucida Sans', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: start\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Trebuchet MS', 'Lucida Sans Unicode', 'Lucida Grande', 'Lucida Sans', Arial, sans-serif\">Make a <strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; scrollbar-width: thin; scrollbar-color: var(--color-scrollbar) var(--color-scrollbar-track);\">Spell Check </strong></span>against each target’s <strong>MD</strong>, and each target makes <strong>Repeated</strong> <strong>Mental</strong> <strong>Save</strong> against your <strong>Spell</strong> <strong>Check</strong>. </p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; scrollbar-width: thin; scrollbar-color: var(--color-scrollbar) var(--color-scrollbar-track); margin: 0.5em 0px; color: rgb(25, 24, 19); font-family: 'Trebuchet MS', 'Lucida Sans Unicode', 'Lucida Grande', 'Lucida Sans', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: start\"><strong>Attack Hit:</strong> The target takes 3 <strong>Divine</strong> <strong>Damage</strong>. </p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; scrollbar-width: thin; scrollbar-color: var(--color-scrollbar) var(--color-scrollbar-track); margin: 0.5em 0px; color: rgb(25, 24, 19); font-family: 'Trebuchet MS', 'Lucida Sans Unicode', 'Lucida Grande', 'Lucida Sans', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: start\"><strong>Save Failure:</strong> The target becomes <strong>Intimidated</strong> of you for 1 minute or until it takes damage.</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; scrollbar-width: thin; scrollbar-color: var(--color-scrollbar) var(--color-scrollbar-track); margin: 0.5em 0px; color: rgb(25, 24, 19); font-family: 'Trebuchet MS', 'Lucida Sans Unicode', 'Lucida Grande', 'Lucida Sans', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: start\"></p><p><em><strong>System Tip: </strong>You can select \"Channel Divinity\" as \"Other Item\" on <strong>Usage</strong> Tab. That way you will use charge of  \"Channel Divinity\"  automatically when using that item.</em></p>",
